-------Misc -----
To check details of a service in COnsul service mesh 
curl -k https://localhost:8501/v1/catalog/service/static-server | jq .

To derigister a given external service:
curl -k --request PUT \
  --header "X-Consul-Token: 019309ecXXXXXXXXXXXXXXc040b3dcd6" https://localhost:8501/v1/catalog/deregister \
  --data '{
    "Datacenter": "tgw",
    "Node": "external-node",
    "ServiceID": "external-service-app"
  }'
